       ================================================================
       Netty is used by AWS SDK v2 for HTTP transport to AWS service
       endpoints. The version is managed by the Spring Boot BOM and is
       the latest available. No higher version resolves these CVEs via
       the current BOM. Re-evaluate on next Spring Boot minor upgrade.
